					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12008401#post-4274583</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12008401/scp-4817#post-4274583</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2019 23:11:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>All the heads have a certain amount of information regarding them that was either only hinted at or straight-up not included in the article. My goal was to paint a picture of a thriving business, without necessarily getting bogged down in its customers.</p> <p>Regarding the 8-seconds&#8230; well, not everybody can afford luxuries, and not everyone knows quite what they're getting into when they sign; <em>especially</em> if they've got nowhere else to turn. They might just end up buying into an existence that isn't quite what it's cracked up to be&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
